                    <title key="Sour cherry puree" type="none"/>
                    <instruction>Nym <ingredient en="sour cherry" commodity="Q68438267">weichsel</ingredient></instruction> vnd <instruction>thu sy In ein
                            <tool en="pot" commodity="Q15711817">haffen</tool></instruction> vnd <instruction>secz auff ein <tool en="ember" commodity="Q177257">glut</tool></instruction> vnd
                        <instruction>laß sy siden</instruction> vnd <instruction>lasz dann kalt
                        werden</instruction> vnd <instruction>streich sy durch ein <tool en="cheesecloth" commodity="Q2621157">tuch</tool></instruction> vnd
                        <instruction>thu sy wider in den <tool en="pot" commodity="Q15711817">hafen</tool></instruction> vnd <instruction>lasz syden</instruction>
                    vnd <instruction>ruer sy wol daz sy sich nit an legen</instruction>
                    <instruction>das tu <time>piß sy dick werd</time></instruction> vnd
                        <instruction>thu dan <ingredient en="honey" commodity="Q10987">honig</ingredient> dar zu</instruction> vnd <instruction><ingredient en="spice" commodity="Q42527">wuercz</ingredient> als gestossen
                            <ingredient en="clove" commodity="Q15622897">negelein</ingredient> vnd
                            <ingredient en="ginger" commodity="Q15046077">yngwer</ingredient> vnd
                        geriben <ingredient en="bread" commodity="Q7802">prot</ingredient></instruction> vnd <instruction>haltz in einem glasirten
                            <tool en="pot" commodity="Q15711817">hafen</tool></instruction>
                    <kitchenTip>Also magstu <alternative reason="dish">von andern sachen <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">salssen</dish> vnd <dish en="electuary" commodity="Q2737588">lattwering</dish> machen</alternative></kitchenTip>
                    <kitchenTip>dann zu der <dish en="electuary" commodity="Q2737588">lattwerig</dish> nym kain <ingredient en="bread" commodity="Q7802" ana="exclusion">prot</ingredient></kitchenTip></div></body></text></TEI>